# Best combined prompt structure

Since you said the **repo will be passed in the prompt itself**, you can also do this in **2 prompts** if you want to reduce latency:

## Prompt 1

User request → intent JSON

## Prompt 2

Intent JSON + repo content → selected components + final code

But I would still recommend **3 prompts** because:

* component selection becomes auditable
* easier to debug wrong choices
* easier to reject hallucinated components
* later easier to replace repo text with indexed retrieval

