# Stronger version of step 2

To reduce hallucination, add this line:

```text
For every selected component, you must justify it using only the provided repository content. If there is insufficient evidence, do not select it.
```

And add this line too:

```text
If you are not certain a component exists, treat it as unavailable.
```

These two lines matter a lot.

